{
  "stem": "13833.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because by that time, the Germans allowed to make a huge, big paper out of this and had it on the walls of Budapest like the king did in Sweden, so everybody could see.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And sure enough, the Germans let people go with this paper, but not the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They killed people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was witnessing one day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was more horror for me than anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because a child, a little child with a star, maybe two and a half-year-old-- and evidently was lost, no parents.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a church.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And out came a Catholic priest, wearing inside his white-- the Hungarian Nazi collar.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he had a revolver.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he saw that little kid and shot him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I felt-- if I just could shoot back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If I can just shoot him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I couldn't do a thing, just picked up the child--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was dead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I took it to Raoul because by that time, Raoul had an orphanage.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I took it there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the child was dead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we couldn't find no identification.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had no idea who it is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to bury it somewhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was-- constantly, you see that all the way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Raoul went-- you see, Eichmann decided to walk the people from Budapest all the way to the Austrian border, what even today in a car is four-and-a-half hours.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was snowing heavily already the end of September.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that's what he wanted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He made trenches, so people died in the trenches.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he didn't take us girls ever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He took diplomats and the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But by that time, he went to the Swiss Red Cross, too, and asked them to help.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
